sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Inference Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway API<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Envoy as Envoy Proxy<br/>ext-proc filter
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelMetrics as Model Server Metrics<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant UDS as UDS Tokenizer<br/>UDS gRPC
    participant ModelServer as Selected Model Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP

    Note over EPP,K8s: Background: EPP watches CRDs
    EPP->>K8s: Watch InferencePool, Pod,<br/>InferenceObjective, InferenceModelRewrite
    K8s-->>EPP: Stream CRD events<br/>SA Bearer token auth

    Note over EPP,ModelMetrics: Background: EPP scrapes metrics (every 50ms)
    EPP->>ModelMetrics: GET /metrics<br/>queue depth, KV cache, running requests
    ModelMetrics-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 1: Inference Request Scheduling
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions
    Gateway->>Envoy: Route via HTTPRoute
    Envoy->>EPP: gRPC ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>(request headers + body)
    EPP->>UDS: Tokenize prompt<br/>(gRPC over Unix Domain Socket)
    UDS-->>EPP: Token IDs
    Note over EPP: Run scheduling pipeline:<br/>1. Filters (ByLabel, SLOHeadroom)<br/>2. Scorers (KVCache, LoadAware,<br/>   PrefixCache, LoRA, Latency)<br/>3. Picker (MaxScore/WeightedRandom)
    EPP-->>Envoy: ProcessingResponse<br/>(inject target-endpoint header)
    Envoy->>ModelServer: Forward request to<br/>selected model server
    ModelServer-->>Envoy: Inference response<br/>(streaming SSE)
    Envoy-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: Streamed response

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2)

    participant PDSidecar as PD Sidecar Proxy<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Prefiller as Prefiller Instance<br/>Dynamic port
    participant Decoder as Local Decoder (vLLM)<br/>8001/TCP HTTP

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions
    Gateway->>Envoy: Route via HTTPRoute
    Envoy->>EPP: gRPC ext-proc
    EPP-->>Envoy: Route to PD sidecar<br/>(prefiller + decoder headers)
    Envoy->>PDSidecar: Forward with routing headers
    PDSidecar->>Prefiller: Prefill request<br/>(HTTP/HTTPS, SSRF allowlist)
    Prefiller-->>PDSidecar: Prefill response<br/>(kv_transfer_params)
    PDSidecar->>Decoder: Decode request with<br/>kv_transfer_params<br/>8001/TCP localhost
    Decoder-->>PDSidecar: Streamed tokens
    PDSidecar-->>Envoy: Streamed response
    Envoy-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: Streamed response

    Note over Client,ModelServer: Flow 3: Encode/Prefill/Decode (E/P/D Multimodal)

    participant Encoder as Encoder Instance<br/>Dynamic port

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(multimodal content)
    Gateway->>Envoy: Route via HTTPRoute
    Envoy->>EPP: gRPC ext-proc
    EPP-->>Envoy: Route to PD sidecar<br/>(encoder + prefiller + decoder headers)
    Envoy->>PDSidecar: Forward with routing headers
    PDSidecar->>Encoder: Encode request (fan-out)<br/>(HTTP/HTTPS, SSRF allowlist)
    Encoder-->>PDSidecar: Encoded representations
    PDSidecar->>Prefiller: Prefill with encoded data<br/>(HTTP/HTTPS, SSRF allowlist)
    Prefiller-->>PDSidecar: Prefill response<br/>(kv_transfer_params)
    PDSidecar->>Decoder: Decode request<br/>8001/TCP localhost
    Decoder-->>PDSidecar: Streamed tokens
    PDSidecar-->>Envoy: Streamed response
    Envoy-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: Streamed response
